{"tid":2388054,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"法國多個城市爆發示威反對整體安全法案，法案內條文包括禁止拍攝警方行動","createTime":"2021-01-30T20:25:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T05:26:20.000Z","uid":79563,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"255d352a89d5438b8f43fe68bb444cb73c7f234d","tid":2388054,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T20:25:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1573241-20210131.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1573241-20210131.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=%2FNwPZCYHbisYOb37lcvQWiUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=39005ad2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1573241-20210131.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=024ac4aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1573241-20210131.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n法國多個城市爆發示威，反對整體安全法案。<br />\n<br />\n示威者不滿法案內條文包括禁止拍攝警方行動，又不滿利用無人機及安裝在街道的攝錄機，進行監控。<br />\n<br />\n法國政府認為，警察成為現實及社交媒體上的攻擊目標，必須配置相關法例。<br />\n<br />\n目擊者表示，在首都巴黎參與的大部分是右翼分子。由於受新型肺炎疫情影響，人數較預期少。在南部蒙彼利埃，估計3000人參與，其餘城市參與的示威者數以百計。<br />\n<br />\n法國的整體安全法案3月將交由國會參議院審議。"},{"pid":"33350fcc4cd45f2b7a0d4cfaeaaf953be43643d5","tid":2388054,"uid":76745,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T20:55:24.000Z","msg":"學到嘢喎馬克隆 唔怪得成日賣水砲車過嚟喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb6494c8b3cd284676ed5b74aea924ca89e83586","tid":2388054,"uid":689,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T20:59:27.000Z","msg":"極權全球化<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fd0d3bdacfae99a6ef54d68679aca00a14b912f","tid":2388054,"uid":78873,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T21:05:00.000Z","msg":"拜登一上台就群魔亂舞"},{"pid":"31ca15a55710d6fb110a76b23ca3fdeb13bf3b32","tid":2388054,"uid":85461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"